    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the bars tho. i was in the bedroom and it was barely there, then i went to the living room and it spiked. but it's not just random... the name is so specific to me. it feels like they're trying to mess with my head or something. do you think they could be using some kind of specialized equipment to pulse the signal or something? like to pinpoint exactly where i'm standing?",
